about.title: [About View]
about.description: KitboxHealth is an innovative platform dedicated to simplifying the process of scheduling medical appointments with the doctors of your preference. Created with the mission of improving access to healthcare, KitboxHealth allows users to find and book appointments with highly qualified healthcare professionals in just a few clicks.
